{"tid":1687124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求援國際，你連罷工嘅決心都無，點幫得落手呀","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T02:09:12.000Z","uid":264079,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15886e0bde8390ade47f3717acc9d1a3bf1ed790","tid":1687124,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"你班友成日想零成本抗爭，癡心妄想<br />\n一日唔無限期罷工，義士都無得罷脫condom 命運<br />\n日日喺度吹奏黃色經濟圈，係好勁，但幫唔幫到被捕義士<br />\n呀？<br />\n<br />\n對家已經無底線，唔順超就扑，粗口，噴椒，實彈，亂鳩咁拉，拉返去性暴力，你哋日L日喺度好嬲，有L用？<br />\n<br />\n1030屯門擅闖屋邨大堂你無反應，<br />\n入東屋台私人地方拉人你無反應<br />\n1031亂扑社工你無反應<br />\n通街非禮，用下體磨女義士你無反應<br />\n<br />\n睇吓智利啦，人哋後發先至啦，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大罷工呀</span></span><br />\n笑鳩緊你啦 ，又求援國際點點點，你連罷工嘅決心都無，幫都幫唔落啦<br />\n<br />\n係呀，對家係超技術，有禁蒙面法，有防起底<br />\n咁又有無法例一定要返工呀，無呀<br />\n<br />\n罷工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c57bb78b81b604f7a8eae083cf3ccb3e19cfe6d","tid":1687124,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"無錢點抗爭啊"},{"pid":"59926b373a50420ba5e8413be782bed8d0bc00ed","tid":1687124,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0735579fc891775380f4e365f013f72f4f0f6eca","tid":1687124,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c57bb78b81b604f7a8eae083cf3ccb3e19cfe6d","tid":1687124,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"無錢點抗爭啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"明唔明咩係大罷工"},{"pid":"b0ccc3c7bc88a63b4b1ffb1229308334059c602e","tid":1687124,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fTVqXu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fTVqXu.gif&h=43055422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"312df9ccc3e02ce5822d469f7ec0